    "summary": "The user is asking for specific advice on which Chicago neighborhoods to avoid to ensure solo safety due to the \"social climate.\" The assistant initially provides upscale suggestions and then, when pushed for specifics, identifies certain areas in the South and West Sides as having higher crime rates and being better to avoid.",
